inale - Corbis/Corbis via Getty Images；Iwi Onodera/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeremy-Allen-White-Bruce-Springsteen-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeremy-Allen-White-Bruce-Springsteen-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeremy-Allen-White-Bruce-Springsteen-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeremy-Allen-White-Bruce-Springsteen-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeremy-Allen-White-Bruce-Springsteen-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jeremy-Allen-White-Bruce-Springsteen-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>杰里米·艾伦·怀特显然一直在给<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>发短信，希望能在伦敦与他见面，为他即将扮演的角色做准备。</p><ul><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944"><b>生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</b></a></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/03/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white-movie-scott-stuber-nebraska-scott-cooper-directing-a24-ellen-goldsmith-vein-1235868961/"><i>Deadline</i></a>报道，怀特是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-reportedly-working-on-film-of-the-making-of-nebraska-3570491">今年一月宣布的</a>电影中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-bear-star-jeremy-allen-white-favourite-bruce-springsteen-nebraska-film-3609892">扮演年轻斯普林​​斯汀的最佳人选，</a>之后四月份宣布<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-bear"><i>由熊</i></a></em>主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-allen-white-to-reportedly-play-bruce-springsteen-in-nebraska-film-3615030">的影片成为该片的一部分</a>。</p><p>据报道，这部电影将探讨斯普林斯汀经典专辑《内布拉斯加》的制作过程。斯科特·库珀（《<em>疯狂的心》、《敌对分子</em>》）将编剧并执导这部电影，该片改编自沃伦·赞恩 2023 年出版的书<i>《从无处拯救我：布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的内布拉斯加的制作》。</i></p><p>现在，为了准备他的角色，怀特向<em>Variety</em>透露，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-at-londons-wembley-stadium-check-out-the-stage-times-3778012">在周六（7 月 27 日）温布利演出</a>前已经“给斯普林斯汀发了短信和电子邮件”。</p><p> “我真的很高兴看到他的表演，”怀特说，并厚颜无耻地补充说斯普林斯汀发短信“像老板一样”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3567516" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3567516" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3567516" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="杰里米·艾伦·怀特" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3567516" class="wp-caption-text">杰里米·艾伦·怀特（Jeremy Allen White）——图片来源：Michael Tran /法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时<em>，备受期待的《熊</em>》第三季刚刚结束，褒贬<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-bear-season-three-getting-mixed-reviews-feels-half-finished-3769123">不一的评论纷至沓来。</a></p><p> <a href="https://amp.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/article/2024/jun/27/the-bear-season-three-review-unbelievably-frustrating" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报</em></a>》的丽贝卡·尼科尔森 (Rebecca Nicholson) 评论了第一集的风格：“顽固的重复是令人信服的故事讲述的敌人。它需要<i>移动</i>。这意味着出色的西德尼（阿约·艾德比里饰）在故事情节以及某种程度上在整个赛季中都被边缘化了。真是浪费啊。”</p><p>艾莉森·赫尔曼在<a href="https://variety.com/2024/tv/tv-reviews/the-bear-season-3-review-fx-1236049732/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》</em></a>中回应道：“它也没有告诉我们任何我们不知道的事情，为大量烹饪传奇人物的客串腾出空间，但却牺牲了故事的发展。该结构适用于长时间的冷开，以建立卡米的情绪；延伸到一整集，这是一种过度的放纵。”</p><p>在布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的其他新闻中，Boss 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-mark-knopfler-star-studded-going-home-teenage-cancer-trust-3601691">参加了马克·诺夫勒 (Mark Knopfler) 众星云集的慈善节目《回家》(Going Home) 的重新录制</a>，该节目的主演包括皇后乐队 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a> ) 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brian-may">布莱恩·梅 (Brian May)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日 (Black Sabbath</a> ) 的托尼·伊奥米 (Tony Iommi)、埃里克·克莱普顿 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eric-clapton">Eric Clapton)</a>等。 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronnie-wood">罗尼·伍德</a>等等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-allen-white-has-been-texting-bruce-springsteen-and-hopes-to-meet-in-london-in-preparation-of-playing-him-in-biopic-3778510">杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 一直在给布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 发短信，希望在伦敦会面，为在传记片中饰演他做准备，这一消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
